6
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:50,840
I trust Li Ya'er.

7
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,200
That's straightforward.

8
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,384
So many disputes and troubles

9
00:00:56,384 --> 00:00:57,560
