10
00:00:58,479 --> 00:00:59,679
I've come to Youzhou

11
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,560
to solve problems,

12
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:03,479
not create new ones.

13
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:11,000
Solve problems?

14
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:12,680
You're the problem.

15
00:01:12,799 --> 00:01:13,680
What should we do?

16
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,400
Please enlighten me.

17
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,159
Li Ya'er

18
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,799
defied my wishes

19
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:19,400
and ruined my decades of planning.

20
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:21,640
That's how you see it?

21
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:23,680
How else should I see it?

22
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,560
Li Ya'er didn't do all this

23
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,319
for me.

24
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,480
He did it to save

25
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,120
his beloved father.

26
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,920
I don't need his salvation.

27
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,799
Tang needs my salvation.

28
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,159
Tang can only save itself

29
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,439
or perish.

30
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,719
What's the point of gaining power?

31
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,120
Can you take it

32
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,200
to your grave?

33
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:49,480
If you were to die now,

34
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,799
any final words?

35
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,719
If you were to die now,

36
00:01:54,719 --> 00:01:56,079
any final words?

37
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:59,280
You're the one who wanted to kill me?

38
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,400
If I want to kill you,

39
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,920
you won't survive.

